01:47:29.765 --> 01:47:30.787
opposition to them.

01:47:31.226 --> 01:47:33.368
You have loved their bad.

01:47:33.788 --> 01:47:36.729
You prefer and have inspected their

01:47:36.770 --> 01:47:37.211
fallacies.

01:47:37.230 --> 01:47:42.774
That's an inside joke that I explained at

01:47:42.814 --> 01:47:43.533
a different show.

01:47:44.354 --> 01:47:45.515
God's got a sense of humor.

01:47:46.435 --> 01:47:50.497
You have consistently contended with

01:47:51.118 --> 01:47:53.840
imposing yourselves over the approach of

01:47:53.880 --> 01:47:54.220
the king.

01:47:55.697 --> 01:48:00.998
calloused, unresponsive, ignorant and fat.

01:48:01.059 --> 01:48:01.578
You see,

01:48:01.759 --> 01:48:05.239
they have contended with imposing

01:48:05.279 --> 01:48:07.261
themselves over the approach of the king.

01:48:07.301 --> 01:48:09.421
It's the very thing that I said.

01:48:10.282 --> 01:48:13.063
They want to preclude his arrival.

01:48:18.069 --> 01:48:21.291
your calloused, unresponsive, ignorant,

01:48:21.310 --> 01:48:21.871
and fat,

01:48:22.430 --> 01:48:24.372
while you have increased and multiplied

01:48:24.391 --> 01:48:26.913
your mixtures and compounds even as

01:48:27.213 --> 01:48:29.774
perfumes to hide your stench.

01:48:31.716 --> 01:48:35.337
Then you dispatch sending out your

01:48:36.238 --> 01:48:39.880
pivoting religious messengers,

01:48:40.581 --> 01:48:45.403
your twisted and idolatrous envoys to

01:48:45.483 --> 01:48:46.984
cause distress and anxiety

01:48:48.407 --> 01:48:51.408
while you besiege on behalf of yourself in

01:48:51.488 --> 01:48:52.648
adversarial fashion,

01:48:54.148 --> 01:48:56.069
doing so as witnesses to yourself

01:48:56.109 --> 01:48:59.149
forevermore, now alienated and estranged,

01:48:59.208 --> 01:49:02.229
as remote, distant,

01:49:02.289 --> 01:49:05.730
and separated as is possible in

01:49:05.791 --> 01:49:06.470
space-time,

01:49:07.990 --> 01:49:13.233
even as you are cast down to Sheowl,

01:49:15.073 --> 01:49:15.252
hell.

01:49:19.345 --> 01:49:22.488
With the many variations of your way and

01:49:22.868 --> 01:49:27.533
prolonged path, you have become worrisome,

01:49:28.113 --> 01:49:28.854
you're tedious,

01:49:29.636 --> 01:49:32.439
but you're never willing to admit that the

01:49:32.859 --> 01:49:35.902
life of the beastly group is hopeless,

01:49:35.962 --> 01:49:37.283
it's futile, it's damning,

01:49:38.363 --> 01:49:40.886
such that you must desist.

01:49:42.738 --> 01:49:43.819
Through your influence,

01:49:43.859 --> 01:49:46.521
you sought to be found sufficient and

01:49:46.561 --> 01:49:49.503
obtained a reason to assert that you were

01:49:49.623 --> 01:49:51.784
somehow not diseased,

01:49:51.805 --> 01:49:53.645
that you were worthy and not afflicted.

01:49:54.686 --> 01:49:57.069
And so by association, who is it?

01:49:58.229 --> 01:49:59.990
And what is the reason?

01:50:01.192 --> 01:50:02.792
Over whom are you so troubled?

01:50:04.613 --> 01:50:06.755
Why are you so riddled with anxiety?

01:50:06.935 --> 01:50:09.337
Why are you dreading everything to the

01:50:09.377 --> 01:50:11.599
point of being frantic, even psychotic?

01:50:12.556 --> 01:50:14.538
while you continue to be so intimidated

01:50:14.578 --> 01:50:16.841
and anxious, awestruck while trembling,

01:50:18.601 --> 01:50:21.344
such that you are so deceptive with your

01:50:21.444 --> 01:50:25.648
outright lies, promoting pagan delusions,

01:50:26.228 --> 01:50:28.130
which are so contrary to reality.

01:50:30.925 --> 01:50:32.907
And therefore it's me you no longer

01:50:32.987 --> 01:50:35.748
mention or remember such that you do not

01:50:35.809 --> 01:50:37.570
recall my most memorable of men.

01:50:38.231 --> 01:50:40.873
You do not even consider these words

01:50:40.934 --> 01:50:41.595
appropriately,

01:50:41.654 --> 01:50:43.336
nor have you taken these statements to

01:50:43.395 --> 01:50:46.198
heart examining this message relative to

01:50:46.219 --> 01:50:48.860
your own motivations.

01:50:48.881 --> 01:50:51.904
So don't question whether I will take

01:50:52.003 --> 01:50:55.587
action even after remaining silent for a

01:50:55.627 --> 01:50:56.127
long while.

01:50:57.823 --> 01:50:59.604
From the very beginning and without end

01:50:59.645 --> 01:51:00.286
regarding me,

01:51:00.326 --> 01:51:02.627
you have never shown any respect.

01:51:05.149 --> 01:51:08.030
I myself will correctly recount and report

01:51:08.110 --> 01:51:10.492
even declare conspicuously publishing and

01:51:10.533 --> 01:51:13.413
making known your sense of righteousness

01:51:13.453 --> 01:51:14.034
and justice,

01:51:14.055 --> 01:51:16.796
your means to decide what is right and

01:51:16.837 --> 01:51:21.380
acquitting even your claims of honesty and

01:51:21.399 --> 01:51:23.440
that which pertains to your activities and

01:51:23.520 --> 01:51:24.061
endeavors,

01:51:24.622 --> 01:51:25.983
the very things you have done

01:51:27.469 --> 01:51:31.711
But neither of these things or those that

01:51:31.730 --> 01:51:33.952
you have gathered to you will be of

01:51:33.992 --> 01:51:36.833
any benefit to you because there is

01:51:36.974 --> 01:51:40.676
nothing that is being accomplished by you.

01:51:41.315 --> 01:51:44.337
And crying out for you,

01:51:44.438 --> 01:51:45.738
summoning others to you,

01:51:45.899 --> 01:51:49.060
or even when issuing a proclamation for

01:51:49.100 --> 01:51:49.300
you,

01:51:50.060 --> 01:51:51.721
why don't you have the others in your

01:51:51.761 --> 01:51:52.221
community,

01:51:52.242 --> 01:51:54.523
those you have assembled to share your

01:51:54.563 --> 01:51:56.444
beliefs, save you.

01:51:58.715 --> 01:52:00.837
Therefore, with regard to all of them,

01:52:01.858 --> 01:52:02.797
the Ruach spirit,

01:52:03.198 --> 01:52:05.159
he will lift up and carry away,

01:52:05.881 --> 01:52:08.182
grasping hold of and taking away the

01:52:08.302 --> 01:52:12.145
meaningless and valueless and those who

01:52:12.225 --> 01:52:13.407
are a waste of breath,

01:52:14.688 --> 01:52:17.090
along with their useless idolatry.

01:52:19.251 --> 01:52:22.594
Yashayah, Isaiah, fifty-seven, thirteen.

01:52:26.109 --> 01:52:28.949
Since sending the 'anan demonic woman and

01:52:29.069 --> 01:52:30.550
Zanah, deceitful whore,

01:52:30.630 --> 01:52:34.751
who is a Shachar betrayer to shield hell

01:52:36.551 --> 01:52:37.612
is a serious outcome.

01:52:38.952 --> 01:52:42.012
Before Yahowah turns to the good guys in

01:52:42.033 --> 01:52:44.212
this story and moves on to address his

01:52:44.253 --> 01:52:46.094
coworkers and their collaboration.

01:52:47.782 --> 01:52:51.649
I'd like to preclude the confusion

01:52:51.708 --> 01:52:53.230
concerning the fate of souls.

01:52:53.331 --> 01:52:55.876
It is germane to know that there are

01:52:55.916 --> 01:52:57.398
three potential outcomes,

01:52:58.059 --> 01:53:00.363
not just the two proposed by religion.

01:53:01.201 --> 01:53:02.141
As we would expect,

01:53:02.681 --> 01:53:04.764
those who have come to know and trust

01:53:04.804 --> 01:53:05.184
Yahowah,

01:53:05.243 --> 01:53:07.645
relying on him by observing his testimony,

01:53:07.985 --> 01:53:09.728
such that they engage in his covenant,

01:53:09.787 --> 01:53:12.270
celebrate the Shabbat and appreciate his

01:53:12.310 --> 01:53:14.731
son by attending his Mowedym,

01:53:15.231 --> 01:53:17.213
they're going to be greeted as family and

01:53:17.253 --> 01:53:18.954
welcomed to heaven by their father.

01:53:19.536 --> 01:53:21.117
There'll be no judgment, no bowing down.

01:53:21.962 --> 01:53:24.463
no review of their words and deeds.

01:53:24.545 --> 01:53:26.826
And while we will inherit everything and

01:53:26.886 --> 01:53:28.506
live forever according to God,

01:53:28.926 --> 01:53:31.108
this is a relatively small group of

01:53:31.148 --> 01:53:31.469
people,

01:53:32.668 --> 01:53:34.109
approximately one in a million

01:53:35.270 --> 01:53:37.971
individuals.

01:53:37.992 --> 01:53:40.694
The second group of souls who will come

01:53:40.734 --> 01:53:41.994
before the judge,

01:53:43.118 --> 01:53:44.618
or more accurately,

01:53:45.539 --> 01:53:46.900
probably his witnesses,

01:53:47.162 --> 01:53:48.502
according to God's testimony,

01:53:48.643 --> 01:53:50.203
they're identified in these words.

01:53:50.845 --> 01:53:53.407
God told us that the record of one's

01:53:53.447 --> 01:53:55.389
beliefs and deeds will be exposed and

01:53:55.448 --> 01:53:58.390
denounced should a person be deemed to

01:53:58.452 --> 01:54:00.713
have worked against him or his people.

01:54:01.413 --> 01:54:03.453
Such souls will be found guilty of

01:54:03.554 --> 01:54:06.475
misleading others through their cultural

01:54:06.515 --> 01:54:09.115
codes, their societal edicts,

01:54:09.176 --> 01:54:10.676
their political platitudes,

01:54:10.695 --> 01:54:12.876
their conspiratorial misconceptions,

01:54:14.436 --> 01:54:15.917
and their religious tomes.

01:54:16.537 --> 01:54:18.597
Their sentence will be to endure eternity

01:54:18.618 --> 01:54:20.778
with like-minded souls incarcerated with

01:54:20.858 --> 01:54:21.358
demons,

01:54:22.297 --> 01:54:25.319
like the ones who have just been denounced

01:54:25.378 --> 01:54:27.179
here forever, separated from Yahowah,

01:54:27.759 --> 01:54:29.899
in Sheowl, the Anan Zanah.

01:54:30.868 --> 01:54:34.274
DP and many of her associates are examples

01:54:34.335 --> 01:54:35.978
of those who will endure a very,

01:54:36.018 --> 01:54:36.979
very dark future.

01:54:37.860 --> 01:54:39.243
But they did this to themselves.

01:54:40.445 --> 01:54:41.287
We ought not pity them.

01:54:42.266 --> 01:54:44.047
The third category of souls who will come

01:54:44.087 --> 01:54:46.390
before the judge are the most numerous.

01:54:46.430 --> 01:54:48.851
They represent some ninety nine point nine

01:54:48.912 --> 01:54:49.972
percent of humanity.

01:54:50.033 --> 01:54:53.234
These mortals will have lived and died not

01:54:53.295 --> 01:54:55.657
knowing Yahowah and therefore Yahowah will

01:54:55.697 --> 01:54:56.278
not know them.

01:54:56.417 --> 01:54:57.979
They will have lived their lives

01:54:58.219 --> 01:55:00.940
uninterested or deceived as to his nature.

01:55:01.721 --> 01:55:03.923
They are the victims of man's religious,

01:55:03.984 --> 01:55:05.664
political and cultural schemes,

01:55:05.944 --> 01:55:07.006
not their advocates.

01:55:07.525 --> 01:55:08.186
These mortals,

01:55:08.226 --> 01:55:10.448
without any spiritual affiliation,

01:55:10.488 --> 01:55:11.810
will simply cease to exist.

01:55:12.707 --> 01:55:14.469
There will be no punishment or reward.

01:55:14.569 --> 01:55:17.210
They lived their lives as they saw fit.

01:55:17.710 --> 01:55:18.729
There will be nothing more.

01:55:18.770 --> 01:55:21.150
Their souls will cease to exist just as

01:55:21.190 --> 01:55:24.533
their bodies succumb and ultimately

01:55:25.193 --> 01:55:25.972
decompose.

01:55:28.493 --> 01:55:30.154
It's a good stopping point because at this

01:55:31.876 --> 01:55:32.676
part of the text,

01:55:33.957 --> 01:55:35.936
God returns to what I would call the

01:55:35.976 --> 01:55:36.978
good guys of his story.

01:55:38.765 --> 01:55:42.088
those advancing his testimony,

01:55:42.869 --> 01:55:44.891
those calling his people home,

01:55:45.773 --> 01:55:48.836
explaining how and when and why and how

01:55:49.376 --> 01:55:52.078
God's going to deliver his promises.

01:55:52.720 --> 01:55:56.042
So we'll return to this place in our

01:55:56.243 --> 01:55:58.364
episode, Returning to the Garden,

01:55:59.185 --> 01:56:00.006
this time tomorrow.

01:56:00.447 --> 01:56:01.228
Thank you for listening.